ED_Title: Zone of peace and cooperation of the South Atlantic
ED_DecisionText: At its 107th plenary meeting, on 16 September 2019, the General Assembly decided to include the item entitled “Zone of peace and cooperation of the South Atlantic” in the draft agenda of its seventy-fourth session.
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the resumed part of the session will be contained in the official record of the GA (A/73/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
